0:00:00.060,0:00:26.580
Zita rangu ndi Chief Ikenna Victor Egbuna.

0:00:26.580,0:00:32.260
Ini ndiri mugari weku Onicha (Nigeria).

0:00:32.260,0:00:47.480
Ini ndiri gweta. Ndiriwo mupi we ma inishuwarenzi pamwe nekuva akautendi.

0:00:47.480,0:01:02.500
Ndauya kuzopa rumbidzo kune WeDenga nokundisimudza kubva munhika kuenda pamusoro pegomo.

0:01:02.500,0:01:12.200
Dambudziko rangu rakatanga muna 1986 pandakadzoka kubva mubasa rangu revechidiki rehurumende.

0:01:12.200,0:01:18.380
Ini ndinobva kumhuri yevanamati vezvifananidzo.

0:01:18.380,0:01:23.680
Ini ndiri muzukuru wemadzishe makuru eheti tsvuku kumhuri mbiri dzese.

0:01:23.680,0:01:29.060
Ndaiva nemakore 9 chete apo baba vangu vakafa.

0:01:29.060,0:01:36.260
Nemhaka yematambudziko mumhuri, ndakava pedyo zvikuru naamai vangu.

0:01:36.260,0:01:43.200
Chaizvoizvo, ndaiwanzodaidzwa kuti bhegi ravo.

0:01:43.200,0:01:46.460
Asi pandakadzoka kubva kubasa re vechidiki,

0:01:46.460,0:01:57.060
rimwe zuva, mumwe wevana babamunini vangu vakauya ndokuudza amai vangu kuti vakaenda kundobvunza n'anga

0:01:57.060,0:02:04.880
kuti vanzwe kuti nei vanhu vemumhuri mangu vachifa vachiri vaduku.

0:02:04.880,0:02:10.280
Mushure memubvunzurudzo, pavakanga vachibva, mukadzi wacho akanga achivadana,

0:02:10.280,0:02:13.700
"Uya, uya! Ikenna, Ikenna!"

0:02:13.700,0:02:15.540
Uye ivo vakabvunza, "Sei?"

0:02:15.540,0:02:19.920
Akati, "Tarira, kune jaya iri mumhuri yako riri gweta.

0:02:19.920,0:02:24.500
Zita rake Ikenna, uye iye achafa! "

0:02:24.500,0:02:28.580
Saka, amai vangu vakatanga kunetseka uye vakabvunza, "Tinoitei?"

0:02:28.580,0:02:31.980
Akati, "Muprisita we chidzimai akati vaifanira kundiunza".

0:02:31.980,0:02:40.840
Saka, vakanditora kumukadzi wacho pamwe nehanzvadzi yangu mukuru, iye akagadzira misanganiswa ye mishonga,

0:02:40.840,0:02:47.640
akashandisa reza kunditemera nyora umo ayiisa mishonga iyoyo mumuviri wangu.

0:02:47.640,0:03:00.540
Kubva pazuva iroro, amai vangu vakandivenga zvakanyanya uye zvose zvandaiita hazvina kugamuchirwa navo.

0:03:00.540,0:03:05.300
Mumabasa angu - Ndakatanga basa rangu segweta -

0:03:05.300,0:03:11.300
muchokwadi, mumwedzi mitanhatu, mukuru wangu akandiudza kuti ndibve pahofisi yake.

0:03:11.300,0:03:16.900
Ndakaedza kuwana imwe nzvimbo yekushanda - ndakashaya.

0:03:16.900,0:03:22.740
Pane imwe nguva, nokuti ndakanga ndichigona masvomhu, ndakatanga kutsvaga chimwe chekuita.

0:03:22.740,0:03:24.980
Ndakatanga kudzidza zve inishuwarenzi.

0:03:24.980,0:03:32.160
Zvakanditorera makore manomwe kuti ndikwanise kuva nhengo ye Chartered Insurance Institute, London.

0:03:32.160,0:03:34.260
Ndakabva ndava Chartered Insurer.

0:03:34.260,0:03:39.080
Ndakatanga kutsvaga mabasa. Ndaizonyorera ndosarudzwa pane vashoma shoma .

0:03:39.080,0:03:46.780
Zuva iro mapepa ekunyorera aizozarurwa, kwaizoonekwa kuti handina kumbo sayinira bepa racho.

0:03:46.780,0:03:52.760
Ndakatsvaga mamwe mabasa - mutevedzeri wa maneja mukuru kuAjaokuta Steel,

0:03:52.760,0:04:00.640
munyori we NJC, mutongi mukuru mudare redzimhosva - panofanira kuva nechinetso chimwe mumafambiro ezvinhu.

0:04:00.640,0:04:05.680
Asi chimwe chinhu chinokosha, ndechekuti pane zvose zvekunyorera kwakadaro,

0:04:05.680,0:04:10.800
Ndaizove nehope - mukadzi wandisingazivi aiuya kuzorara neni.

0:04:10.800,0:04:17.540
Mushure maizvozvi, zvose pamusoro pezvinhu izvozvo zvaizoenda.

0:04:17.540,0:04:29.560
Izvo zvakaramba zvichienderera kusvikira ndanzwa nezve SCOAN, uye ndakauya kuzosangana nomunhu wa Mwari.

0:04:29.560,0:04:38.840
Pandakasangana naye chiso ne chiso, akandipa Morning Water iyi ne kabhuku aka

0:04:38.840,0:04:53.060
rakanzi 'What The Future Holds'. Akarisaina ndokuripa kwandiri.

0:04:53.060,0:05:08.040
Kubvira pazuva iroro, zvandakarongerwa muhupenyu zvakatanga rwendo rwekudzorerwa.

0:05:08.040,0:05:14.240
Kare, ndaizoenda kudare redzimhosva, ndoshanda pane nyaya yacho zvakanaka asi ndisingakwanisi kubhadharwa mari.

0:05:14.240,0:05:19.800
Mune zvimwe zviitiko, handaikwanisa kuwana chero peni.

0:05:19.800,0:05:33.300
Gare gare, nekushanyira pa SCOAN, ini ndakanga ndisisaone chero munhu wandisingazive achiuya kuzorara neni.

0:05:33.300,0:05:37.960
Ini ndakanosiya magwaro ezve inishuwarenzi ne akaunzi

0:05:37.960,0:05:44.720
uye ndokudzokera kubasa rangu repakutanga - basa rezve ugweta.

0:05:44.720,0:05:50.220
Humwe husiku, mushure mokunyengetera nemunhu wa Mwari pa sikirini

0:05:50.220,0:05:54.540
uye kushandisa Morning Water, ndakamuona muhope.

0:05:54.540,0:05:58.340
Ndakazviwana ndiri muhofisi yangu yekutanga.

0:05:58.340,0:06:02.520
Ndakaona kuti ndaive ndirere ndakapera simba muhofisi

0:06:02.520,0:06:05.820
uye chinochengeta chacho chakakiiwa nemakiyi anenge matatu.

0:06:05.820,0:06:09.000
Ndakanga ndapfigirwa mukati mehofisi iyoyo.

0:06:09.000,0:06:12.240
Zvino munhu wa Mwari akauya.

0:06:12.240,0:06:16.120
Pandakamuona, ndakasvetuka, "Munhu wa Mwari! Munhu wa Mwari!"

0:06:16.120,0:06:26.900
Akangovhura makii akandiudza kuti ndibude.

0:06:26.900,0:06:29.680
Uye ndakabuda.

0:06:29.680,0:06:40.440
Kubva pazuva iroro, ramangwana rangu rakatanga rwendo rwekudzoserwa nekukurumidza

0:06:40.440,0:06:53.600
Uye nhasi, ini ndiri Mumiriri Mukuru we Nigeria.

0:06:53.600,0:06:59.880
Iri ndiro basa repamusoro-soro raungawane mune zve basa rezvemutemo.

0:06:59.880,0:07:11.700
Ndakagadzwa musi wa 18, September, 2017.

0:07:11.700,0:07:19.060
Pabepa, riri pa bhodhi, ini ndiri Nhamba 7,

0:07:19.060,0:07:24.100
