0:07:24.100,0:07:33.840
Vanhu vanopfuura 500 vakanyorera, 169 ndivo vakasarudzwa pakutanga asi 30 chete ndivo vakagadzwa.

0:07:33.840,0:07:41.680
Uye ini ndiri Nhamba 7 pakati pavo.

0:07:41.680,0:07:52.760
Mifananidzo yamunoona pano ndini ndakapfeka zvose zve Mumiriri Mukuru we Nigeria.

0:07:52.760,0:08:01.160
