0:08:26.320,0:08:34.440
Ndakadanwa ku benji revana gweta muna 1985. Ichi ndicho chitupa changu.

0:08:34.440,0:08:38.600
Ndakava umwe we Chartered Insurance Institute, London.

0:08:38.600,0:08:42.380
